trans-unit.source: Defines additional management capabilities for the application and extraction of personalization state.
trans-unit.target: Definierar ytterligare hanteringsfunktioner för programmet och extrahering av anpassningstillståndet.

trans-unit.source: In addition to using the `Personalizable` attribute on control properties, a control can also implement IPersonalizable for additional management capabilities for the application and extraction of personalization state.
trans-unit.target: Förutom att använda den `Personalizable` attributet för kontrollegenskaper kan en kontroll även implementera IPersonalizable för ytterligare hanteringsfunktioner för programmet och extrahering av anpassningstillståndet.

trans-unit.source: For example, controls that need to manage private state information should implement this interface.
trans-unit.target: Kontroller som behöver kunna hantera privata statusinformation bör till exempel implementera gränssnittet.

trans-unit.source: Controls that access personalized data through complex mechanisms, such as custom cache solutions, data persistence to mainframes, or XML Web services, should also implement this interface.
trans-unit.target: Kontroller som åtkomst till personliga data via komplexa sätt, till exempel anpassade cache-lösningar, -datapersistence stordatorer eller XML-webbtjänster bör också implementera gränssnittet.

trans-unit.source: > [!IMPORTANT] > You should not add types based on classes defined in the App_Code directory and then depend on the default binary serialization mechanism.
trans-unit.target: > [!IMPORTANT] > Bör du inte lägga till typer som baseras på klasser som definieras i katalogen App_Code och sedan beror på standardmekanism för binär serialisering.

trans-unit.source: App_Code-based artifacts are not consistently binary-serializable due to the fact that they can have their assembly names changed at random points in time.
trans-unit.target: App_Code-baserade artefakter är inte konsekvent binary-serialiserbara på att de kan ha sina sammansättningsnamn ändras vid slumpässiga intervall i tid.

trans-unit.source: Gets a value that indicates whether the custom data that a control manages has changed.
trans-unit.target: Hämtar ett värde som anger om anpassade data som hanteras av en kontroll har ändrats.

trans-unit.source: When data managed by a control has changed, the control is considered "dirty."
trans-unit.target: När data som hanteras av en kontroll har ändrats anses kontrollen "ändrade".

trans-unit.source: A control should return `true` if the custom data that it manages through the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.IPersonalizable> interface has changed.
trans-unit.target: En kontroll ska returnera `true` om anpassade data som den hanterar via den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.IPersonalizable>gränssnitt har ändrats.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.IPersonalizable>

trans-unit.source: If a control returns `true` from this property, the control's <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.IPersonalizable.Save%2A> interface method implementation is called during property value extraction.
trans-unit.target: Om en kontroll returnerar `true` från den här egenskapens, kontrollen <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.IPersonalizable.Save%2A>implementeringsgränssnittet-metoden anropas under Extraheringen av värdet för egenskapen.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.IPersonalizable.Save%2A>

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > This property is checked automatically by the personalization infrastructure during the latter phases of processing a POST request.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > Den här egenskapen kontrolleras automatiskt infrastrukturen som anpassning under senare faserna i en POST-begäran bearbetades.

trans-unit.source: However, for GET requests, the value returned from the IsDirty property is not checked.
trans-unit.target: Men för GET-begäranden kontrolleras det värde som returneras från egenskapen IsDirty inte.

trans-unit.source: Some other event has to have caused the control to be considered "dirty" for any control state--not just data managed by <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.IPersonalizable>--to be saved.
trans-unit.target: Vissa andra händelsen har har orsakat kontrollen anses vara "ändrade" för alla kontrollens status – inte bara data som hanteras av <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.IPersonalizable>--ska sparas.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.IPersonalizable>

trans-unit.source: If a control can mark itself as "dirty" during a GET request, or if the personalization infrastructure under some very specific boundary conditions considers a control "dirty" during a GET request, then <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.IPersonalizable.Save%2A> will always be called.
trans-unit.target: Om en kontroll kan markera sig själv som "felaktigt" under en GET-begäran, eller om anpassning infrastruktur under vissa mycket specifik gränsvillkor anser att en kontroll "ändrade" under en GET-begäran sedan <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.IPersonalizable.Save%2A>alltid anropas.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.IPersonalizable.Save%2A>

trans-unit.source: A control can reference its associated <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager> control and check the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartPersonalization.Scope%2A> property to determine the current scope.
trans-unit.target: En kontroll kan referera till dess associerade <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager>styr och kontrollera den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartPersonalization.Scope%2A>egenskapen fastställa den aktuella omfattningen.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartPersonalization.Scope%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager>

trans-unit.source: The "dirty" state of a control's custom data should be appropriate for the current scope.
trans-unit.target: "Felaktig" tillståndet för anpassade data för en kontroll ska vara lämplig för den aktuella omfattningen.

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> if the custom data managed with the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.IPersonalizable"></xref> interface has changed; otherwise, <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>Om anpassade data hanteras med den <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.IPersonalizable"> </xref> gränssnitt har ändrats, annars <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Loads custom data into a control.
trans-unit.target: Läser in anpassade data i en kontroll.

trans-unit.source: This method is called on a control to allow it to load custom data into itself.
trans-unit.target: Den här metoden anropas på en kontroll för att läsa in anpassade data till sig själv.

trans-unit.source: It can also return a value that indicates whether a control's custom state must be written back to the underlying data store, regardless of whether any other personalization data on the page has changed.
trans-unit.target: Det kan också returnera ett värde som anger om anpassade tillstånd för en kontroll måste skrivas tillbaka till den underliggande databasen, oavsett om andra anpassningsdata på sidan har ändrats.

trans-unit.source: A control can set its own custom properties and carry out additional internal logic based on the values contained in the personalization dictionary.
trans-unit.target: En kontroll kan ange sina egna anpassade egenskaper och utföra ytterligare internt baserat på de värden som finns i ordlistan anpassning.

trans-unit.source: This method is called by the Web Parts control set while applying personalization data to a control.
trans-unit.target: Den här metoden anropas av kontrollen webbdelar som angavs vid tillämpa anpassningsdata på en kontroll.

trans-unit.source: You should also be aware of the merge behavior of <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PersonalizationScope>-scoped versus <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PersonalizationScope>-scoped properties contained in the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PersonalizationDictionary> object.
trans-unit.target: Du bör också vara medveten om merge beteendet för <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PersonalizationScope>-omfång jämfört med <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PersonalizationScope>-omfång egenskaperna i den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PersonalizationDictionary>objekt.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PersonalizationDictionary> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PersonalizationScope> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PersonalizationScope>

trans-unit.source: The `state` parameter contains a merged representation of custom data that was loaded from the underlying data store.
trans-unit.target: Den `state` parametern innehåller en sammanfogad representation av anpassade data som har lästs in från underliggande datalagret.

trans-unit.source: In <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PersonalizationScope> scope, all the values that were previously added when the page itself was in <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PersonalizationScope> scope would be available.
trans-unit.target: I <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PersonalizationScope>omfång genom alla värden som tidigare lades när själva sidan i <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PersonalizationScope>scope är tillgänglig.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PersonalizationScope> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PersonalizationScope>

trans-unit.source: In <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PersonalizationScope> scope, if a value associated with <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PersonalizationScope> personalization scope had one value added when the page was in <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PersonalizationScope> scope, and a different value when the page was in <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PersonalizationScope> scope, then the personalization infrastructure would only include the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PersonalizationScope>-scoped value (as opposed to the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PersonalizationScope> scope value) within the `state` parameter.
trans-unit.target: I <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PersonalizationScope>räckvidd, om ett värde som är associerat med <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PersonalizationScope>anpassningsläge hade ett värde som har lagts till när sidan var i <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PersonalizationScope>omfång och ett annat värde när sidan i <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PersonalizationScope>omfånget och sedan anpassning infrastruktur kan bara innehålla den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PersonalizationScope>-omfång värde (inte den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PersonalizationScope>omfång värde) inom den `state` parameter.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PersonalizationScope> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PersonalizationScope> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PersonalizationScope> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PersonalizationScope> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PersonalizationScope> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PersonalizationScope>

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PersonalizationDictionary"></xref> that contains custom scoped data that was loaded from the underlying data store.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PersonalizationDictionary"> </xref> som innehåller anpassade begränsade data som har lästs in från underliggande datalagret.

trans-unit.source: Saves custom properties and internal state information in the control's <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PersonalizationDictionary"></xref> object.
trans-unit.target: Anpassade egenskaper och interna statusinformation sparas i kontrollens <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PersonalizationDictionary"> </xref> objekt.

trans-unit.source: A server control can store its own custom properties and internal state information the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PersonalizationDictionary> specified in the `state` parameter.
trans-unit.target: En serverkontroll kan lagra sina egna anpassade egenskaper och interna statusinformation den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PersonalizationDictionary>anges i den `state` parameter.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PersonalizationDictionary>

trans-unit.source: The information is stored as a series of name/value pairs.
trans-unit.target: Informationen lagras som en serie namn/värde-par.

trans-unit.source: It is the responsibility of the control to use name/value pairs that it can recognize during subsequent calls made to the control through the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.IPersonalizable.Load%2A> method.
trans-unit.target: Ansvarar för kontrollen att använda namn/värde-par som den kan hantera under efterföljande anrop till kontrollen via den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.IPersonalizable.Load%2A>metoden.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.IPersonalizable.Load%2A>

trans-unit.source: A control can reference its associated <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager> control and check the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PersonalizationScope> object to determine the current scope.
trans-unit.target: En kontroll kan referera till dess associerade <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager>styr och kontrollera den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PersonalizationScope>objektet för att avgöra den aktuella omfattningen.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PersonalizationScope> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager>

trans-unit.source: Custom state information should be appropriate for the current scope.
trans-unit.target: Information om anpassade tillstånd bör vara relevanta för den aktuella omfattningen.

trans-unit.source: Note that each <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PersonalizationEntry> value that is added to the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PersonalizationDictionary> object should be associated with the appropriate scope value, because the personalization infrastructure depends on this when merging <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PersonalizationScope> and <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PersonalizationScope>-scoped custom data prior to passing it to the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.IPersonalizable.Load%2A> method.
trans-unit.target: Observera att varje <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PersonalizationEntry>värde som läggs till i <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PersonalizationDictionary>objektet ska vara associerat med lämpligt scope-värde eftersom anpassning infrastruktur beror på den här vid sammanfogning av <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PersonalizationScope>och <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PersonalizationScope>-omfång anpassade data innan du skickar det till den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.IPersonalizable.Load%2A>metoden.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.IPersonalizable.Load%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PersonalizationScope> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PersonalizationScope> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PersonalizationDictionary> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PersonalizationEntry>

trans-unit.source: When using the standard ASP.NET implementation of Web Parts, controls must ensure that objects placed in the state dictionary can be serialized by the ASP.NET <xref:System.Web.UI.ObjectStateFormatter> class.
trans-unit.target: När du använder vanliga ASP.NET-implementeringen av webbdelar kontroller måste se till att objekt som placerats i ordlistan tillstånd kan serialiseras av ASP.NET- <xref:System.Web.UI.ObjectStateFormatter>klass.</xref:System.Web.UI.ObjectStateFormatter>

trans-unit.source: In practice, this means the following: - Primitive .NET Framework types, strings, and collection-oriented .NET Framework types such as arrays, array lists, hash tables, and hybrid dictionaries, are automatically serializable.
trans-unit.target: I praktiken innebär det innebär följande:-primitiva .NET Framework typer, strängar och samling indatavärdena .NET Framework-typer som matriser, matris listor, hash-tabeller och hybrid ordlistor är automatiskt serialiseras.

trans-unit.source: - Custom types that supply their own <xref:System.ComponentModel.TypeConverter> classes capable of serializing to and deserializing from strings are considered serializable.
trans-unit.target: -Anpassade typer som tillhandahåller egna <xref:System.ComponentModel.TypeConverter>klasser kan till serialisering och avserialisering av från strängar betraktas som serialiserbar.</xref:System.ComponentModel.TypeConverter>

trans-unit.source: - Custom types that can be serialized by the <xref:System.Runtime.Serialization.Formatters.Binary.BinaryFormatter> class are considered serializable.
trans-unit.target: -Anpassade typer som kan serialiseras av den <xref:System.Runtime.Serialization.Formatters.Binary.BinaryFormatter>klassen betraktas som serialiserbar.</xref:System.Runtime.Serialization.Formatters.Binary.BinaryFormatter>

trans-unit.source: > [!IMPORTANT] > You should not add types based on classes defined in the App_Code directory and then depend on the default binary serialization mechanism.
trans-unit.target: > [!IMPORTANT] > Bör du inte lägga till typer som baseras på klasser som definieras i katalogen App_Code och sedan beror på standardmekanism för binär serialisering.

trans-unit.source: App_Code-based artifacts are not consistently binary-serializable due to the fact that they can have their assembly names changed at random points in time.
trans-unit.target: App_Code-baserade artefakter är inte konsekvent binary-serialiserbara på att de kan ha sina sammansättningsnamn ändras vid slumpässiga intervall i tid.

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PersonalizationDictionary"></xref> that contains custom scoped data that was loaded from the underlying data store.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PersonalizationDictionary"> </xref> som innehåller anpassade begränsade data som har lästs in från underliggande datalagret.
